snippet.title: 100% Orange Juice - Sweet Breaker Character Trailer
snippet.description:
Sweet Breaker (VA: Kiritani Choucho 桐谷蝶々) character and announcer voice is now available in 100% Orange Juice - Breaker Pack on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/465480/100_Orange_Juice__Breaker_Pack/

100% Orange Juice is a digital multiplayer board game populated by developer Orange Juice's all-star cast. Characters from Flying Red Barrel, QP Shooting, Suguri and Sora come together with all-new characters to duke it out... with dice.
